name: Alliance XR Culture Gallery
summary: Come experience the first exhibition, a work-in-progress called ANCESTRAL FUTURISM: UNAPOLOGETICALLY MELANATED (avirtual exploration of the Mythic + da Truth!).  Visitors to the XR Culture Gallery will experience works of art by Catherine Blackburn, Lola Flash, Jessi Jumanji, Karo Duro, and Valentina Vargas – and many others to follow.  We co-created this space with the hope of building access to technology for those traditionally excluded from opportunity. We share a great resistance to participating...
